Liwiidae is a family of nektaspid (stem-group chelicerate) in the order Nektaspida. Below are the genera and species of this family:

Buenaspis Budd, 1999Buenaspis forteyi  Budd, 1999Liwia Dzik and Lendzion, 1988Liwia plana Lendzion, 1975
Liwia convexa Lendzion, 1975Soomaspis Fortey & Theron, 1995Soomaspis splendida Fortey & Theron, 1995Tariccoia Hammann et al., 1990Tariccoia arrusensis Hammann et al., 1990